    <p>
      This year we're going bigger. More teams, more money for charity, more fun! $3,000 buy in to enter competition, all funds will go to charity. This year we can have 24 teams competing, for a total of $72k raised!
    </p>
    <h3>What?</h3>
    <p>
    GitHub employees and a number of victims from other teams participate in an epic Dodgeball tournament.  Each team that is entered donates at least $3000 to the charity pot. At the end, all of the donations will be split between 4 pre-choosen charities. In the process, thousands are entertained.
    </p>
    <h3>How?</h3>
    <p>We will be playing (roughly) by the <a href="http://dodgeball4ever.com/balls/rules-staypuft-hollywood">rules of the World Dodgeball Society</a>.  The only difference being that the female:male ratio has been relaxed for these games.
    </p>
