        <tr>
          <td valign="top" nowrap><a href="http://www.shfb.org/home">Second Harvest Food Bank</a></td>
          <td class="desc">Mobilizes individuals, companies, and community partners to connect people to the nutritious food they need.</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </p>
